    "headline": "Xfinity and Comcast Business High-Speed Internet Now Available to More Than 2,100 Previously Unserved Homes and Businesses in Central Indiana",
    "summary": "INDIANAPOLIS, May 05, 2026--Together with the Indiana Broadband Office, Comcast announced the completion of construction to connect more than 2,100 new homes and businesses in counties across Central Indiana to high-speed Internet from Xfinity and Comcast Business. Communities in Hendricks, Wayne, Allen and Delaware counties now join 65 million homes and businesses nationwide with access to a network that fuels innovation, productivity, and everyday connection.",
